OL,3,CHow Reeves has found an additional
OL,4,C#50bn a year to borrow
OL,6,FBy targetting the "snuffle," Rachel
OL,7,FReeves is creating "headroom" to
OL,8,Fborrow an additional #50bn to #60bn
OL,9,Fevery year - which is more than the
OL,10,Funfunded borrowing that spooked
OL,11,Finvestors in Liz Truss's mini-budget
OL,12,Fand led to a fiscal crisis.
OL,14,FSo, whether the chancellor is being
OL,15,Fsensible or reckless by changing the
OL,16,Fdebt target in next week's budget,
OL,17,Fwill be decided by the "guard rails"
OL,18,For constraints she puts in place.
OL,20,FI assume the reaction of many of you
OL,21,Fis "You what?"
