OL,3,CHow Reeves has found an additional
OL,4,C#50bn a year to borrow
OL,6,FSo this is why the snuffle matters.
OL,8,FIt is about whether Reeves is creating
OL,9,Fspace for the government to borrow to
OL,10,Ffund productive investment, that will
OL,11,Fboost economic growth which makes us
OL,12,Fricher.
OL,14,FOr whether she is recklessly robbing
OL,15,FPeter to pay Paul, at a time when the
OL,16,Fnational debt and interest payments
OL,17,Fare high.
OL,19,FNow to define the "snuffle"
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
