OL,3,CHow Reeves has found an additional
OL,4,C#50bn a year to borrow
OL,6,FThe "snuffle" is "public sector net
OL,7,Ffinancial liabilities", or PSNFL
OL,8,F("snuffle" with a silent "p", as in
OL,9,F"Psmith").
OL,11,FOvernight in Washington at IMF
OL,12,Fmeetings, the Chancellor signalled she
OL,13,Fwould be targetting PSNFL in her
OL,14,Fduality of fiscal rule, in place of
OL,15,Fthe inherited target - which is public
OL,16,Fsector net debt excluding the Bank of
OL,17,FEngland.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
