OL,3,CHow Reeves has found an additional
OL,4,C#50bn a year to borrow
OL,6,FThe simple way to understand the
OL,7,Fdifference is that public sector net
OL,8,Fdebt is gross debt, minus some super
OL,9,Fliquid investments, whereas PSNFL
OL,10,Fsubtracts a greater range and larger
OL,11,Fstock of assets.
OL,13,FPSNFL is not a brand-new concept. It
OL,14,Fis already measured by the Office for
OL,15,FNational Statistics.
OL,17,FAnd like all these accounting or
OL,18,Fsocial constructs, its importance lies
OL,19,Fin whether it helps to keep the
OL,20,Fgovernment honest, or is it a tool for
OL,21,Fdodgy ministerial cover-ups.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
