OL,3,CHow Reeves has found an additional
OL,4,C#50bn a year to borrow
OL,6,FThe problem with the target Reeves
OL,7,Finherited from her predecessor Jeremy
OL,8,FHunt, is that it gives her almost no
OL,9,F"headroom" to borrow to fund
OL,10,Finvestment.
OL,12,FPSNFL creates this headroom - as if by
OL,13,Fmiracle - in two ways.
OL,15,FThe impact of including the value of
OL,16,Fthe student loan book is the more
OL,17,Fimportant miracle of these two.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
