OL,3,CHow Reeves has found an additional
OL,4,C#50bn a year to borrow
OL,6,FThe question is whether seeing the
OL,7,Fliabilities as a snuffle is more
OL,8,Frational than the current picture.
OL,10,FI would say yes, to an extent.
OL,12,FOn the positive side, the adoption of
OL,13,FPSNFL will allow Reeves to invest
OL,14,Fbillions of pounds every year - in
OL,15,Ftransport, power generation and
OL,16,Felectricity networks - through her
OL,17,FNational Wealth Fund and GB Energy,
OL,18,Fand in partnership with the private
OL,19,Fsector, relatively unconstrained by
OL,20,Fher debt target.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
