OL,3,CHow Reeves has found an additional
OL,4,C#50bn a year to borrow
OL,6,FThe reason is that under the PSNFL
OL,7,Fdefinitions, the value of equity
OL,8,Finvestments in private companies is
OL,9,Fdeducted from debt.
OL,11,FHowever, if the government were to own
OL,12,F100% of an investment project, in the
OL,13,Fway it typically does, then the value
OL,14,Fof that investment would not be netted
OL,15,Foff PSNFL.
OL,17,FOr to put it another way, adopting
OL,18,FPSNFL does not allow for an unlimited
OL,19,Finvestment bonanza.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
