OL,3,CHow Reeves has found an additional
OL,4,C#50bn a year to borrow
OL,6,FThere will be nothing like a glut for
OL,7,Fpublic services.
OL,9,FApart from anything else, if markets
OL,10,Fwere to decide, when all the detail is
OL,11,Fpublished next Wednesday, that Reeves
OL,12,Fdoes want to raid a near-bottomless
OL,13,Fpurse, that would be a disaster.
OL,15,FDebt in the UK - and throughout the
OL,16,Frich developed world - is at very high
OL,17,Flevels for peacetime, and when growth
OL,18,Fis not generating the tax revenues
OL,19,Fneeded to fund the public services we
OL,20,Fbelieve we deserve.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
