OL,11,FTherefore, if investors were to fear
OL,12,Fthat the additional debt Reeves will
OL,13,Fincur will not spur growth, and
OL,14,Finstead will be more money down the
OL,15,Fdrain, they won't want to lend to her.
OL,17,FAnd we'll find ourselves in the Truss/
OL,18,FKwarteng vicious cycle of interest
OL,19,Frates being forced up and choking off
OL,20,Fdesperately needed economic momentum.
